Package: btrbk
Architecture: all
Depends: perl, btrfs-tools (>= 3.18.2), ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: openssh-client
Description: tool for creating snapshots and remote backups of btrfs
 subvolumes Backup tool for btrfs subvolumes, using a configuration
 file, allows creation of backups from multiple sources to multiple
 destinations, with ssh and flexible retention policy support (hourly,
 daily, weekly, monthly).
